    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865750/extras/e0ceacd36953cef6d4e730348ca4a769.avif?t=1768133349\" width=618 height=184 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i><strong>FAYE FALLING</strong></i> you play as a recently passed soul, unable to recall who they are, or how they died. After a chance encounter with a powerful entity, you begin <strong>an epic journey to defeat a growing darkness</strong>, while recovering your memories along the way...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865750/extras/8d12b6478b7ec2b3541bedb959b1df6e.avif?t=1768133349\" width=618 height=69 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865750/extras/6e5979701dcb12d54624b42519c88e85.poster.avif?t=1768133349\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865750/extras/6e5979701dcb12d54624b42519c88e85.webm?t=1768133349\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865750/extras/6e5979701dcb12d54624b42519c88e85.mp4?t=1768133349\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in fun, fast-paced <strong>turn-based battles</strong> against a large variety of enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Evade damage</strong> by dodging enemy attacks in quick, snappy minigames. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cast powerful spells</strong> to fight your opponents and protect yourself.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865750/extras/c198f1320a46ca83d75e01064ad58489.avif?t=1768133349\" width=618 height=69 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865750/extras/4b4197995dd7a49993ff652a2b0b9bda.poster.avif?t=1768133349\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865750/extras/4b4197995dd7a49993ff652a2b0b9bda.webm?t=1768133349\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865750/extras/4b4197995dd7a49993ff652a2b0b9bda.mp4?t=1768133349\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore a diverse, ethereal world,</strong> filled with minigames, puzzles and secrets.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete <strong>optional side quests</strong> to receive rare items and gear.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865750/extras/02e3b1eda707e0435a8d86eae0b8e309.avif?t=1768133349\" width=618 height=69 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865750/extras/89bd3cbaa78363a5fdb5093e4c7168d9.poster.avif?t=1768133349\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865750/extras/89bd3cbaa78363a5fdb5093e4c7168d9.webm?t=1768133349\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865750/extras/89bd3cbaa78363a5fdb5093e4c7168d9.mp4?t=1768133349\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead a <strong>path of darkness</strong>, where you'll steal, kill and grow horns, <strong>or a path of light</strong>, where you'll spread hope and sprout a glowing halo.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet <strong>several strange characters</strong> along your journey; from an anxious skull, to a trio of divine angels. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make significant narrative choices that'll lead you toward <strong>multiple endings</strong>. <i>(Including a hidden true ending.)</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock a New Game+</strong> mode with increased difficulty, and additional lore.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Faye Falling is an emotional gameplay experience that explores death, suffering and meaning.</i> It was made entirely by one person: me!</p>",
